01:55:27.399 --> 01:55:33.878
Incoming livestream: untrusted repository, when opened, should have all the coding executing features disabled.

37
01:55:33.999 --> 01:55:42.049
Incoming livestream: And also, if the workspace config changes in the future, there should be a reprompt… the trust should be reprompt to the user.

